verbose_text: Finally, the results showed that a 2%-SD, a 4%-SD and an 8%-SD significantly increased the MDA level (P < 0.01, P < 0.01, P < 0.05, respectively), and exercise training significantly decreased the MDA level of the 0%-SD flies, 2%-SD flies and 4%-SD flies (P < 0.05), but the MDA level of the 8%-SD flies did not change significantly after exercise training (P> 0.05) (XREF_FIG D).
